function.name: provide_validation_feedback
function.description:
Feedback about the outcome of the sequence of validation
attempts. This should be the last call made after a sequence of
validation calls for the same address, and should be called once
the transaction is concluded. This should only be sent once for
the sequence of ``ValidateAddress`` requests needed to validate
an address fully.
